      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CONCILIATE (5) is two from two when second up so will be improved by her resuming effort against a handy line-up at Menangle. Has recorded two wins and a placing from three tries at this circuit and distance so looks well placed. BETWEEN DECKS (4) is really delivering now having broken his maiden two back before delivering again last week at Penrith, cruising home by more than 10m. Led in both of those wins and can push forward again from this draw. Big chance to land the hat trick. THIS IS HEAVEN (2) has come from wide barriers in two city starts off a spell. Goes well third-up and and has good statistics at this circuit and distance so can improve plenty from the good draw. JILLIBY AMIGO (6) was runner-up in a higher-graded race last week and while drawn wider he won from a similar draw three back at this circuit and distance.",
